<HEADLINE>
ST. HILDEGARD: MEDIEVAL NUN IS NEW-AGE POP ICON  
 
</HEADLINE>
  
 (ATTN: Religion Editors - note Sept. 17 feast day)   (RESENDING from Aug. 27 for those needing)  
  
 (This intriguing ``separate buy'' article is from the International
Herald Tribune.)  
  
