 &HT;    Here is a sampling of great places and tours for your holiday
trip:
 &HT;     _ Saga Holidays,  which packages tours just for those 49-plus,
has a special Christmas in London tour for singles and a Danube
River Christmas cruise. Also on its menu of holiday destinations
are old favorites such as Palm Springs, Calif., and San Antonio,
Texas. Many of its trips do not require a single supplement.
 &HT;    The London tour features a walking tour of Dickensian London,
