   &UR; Other financial &LR;
</P>
<P>
   KOREA-KIA-AUCTION (Detroit) _ South Korea's auction of Kia
Motors and its affiliate, Asia Motors, is likely to collapse
because of debt write-offs demanded by the bidders. All four
bidders, Ford, Samsung Motors, Daewoo Motor and Hyundai Motor,
ignored creditors' requests to alter their bidding conditions by
the deadline today, Kia says. By Keith Bradsher.
</P>
