   The Seattle Post-Intelligencer plans to move the following
stories for clients of the NYTimes News Service for editions of
Tuesday, Sept. 1, and thereafter. If you have any questions, please
call Tina May at (206) 448-8355.
</P>
<P>
   FILMMAKERS-VANCOUVER (Vancouver, B.C.) Who needs X-Files when
you have a declining dollar, a burgeoning talent pool, real
Hollywood studios and a government that bends over backwards at the
mention of a new shoot? A look at Vancouver's booming film biz.
</P>
<P>
   By M.L. Lyke. (story will move in the ``e'' category)
