run
</P>
<P>
   3.Smart-ass babysitter who asks, `Which one of you is Sneezy?'
</P>
<P>
   2.When dad's in a hurry and puts four of us in the same diaper
</P>
<P>
   1.Birthday presents marked `To whom it may concern'
