</P>
<P>
   FORT WORTH, Texas _ Eight months after Texans were finally
allowed to tap the value of their homes for extra cash, the No. 1
use of the home equity loans is not to start a business, put a
child through college or improve the homestead. Instead, it's debt
consolidation _ rolling up the outstanding balances on credit
cards, personal loans and other pricey obligations and paying them
off with one, less-expensive home-equity loan. By JIM FUQUAY. Story
will move in ``f'' financial category. &QL; 
