<P>
   BOX-HOLYFIELD-TRAINING _ ATLANTA _ Like many other Atlantans,
Evander Holyfield is working at home these days. He gets up before
dawn to train in his personal gym for the Sept. 19 bout against
Vaughn Bean at the Georgia Dome, and squeezes in the occasional
parental duty in between workouts at his estate in Fairburn. He and
personal trainer Tim Hallmark are bunking in the unfinished but
livable mansion while Holyfield's wife and children stay in the
existing home. (Schultz, Atlanta Journal-Constitution) WITH PHOTOS.
ETA 8 p.m. ET.
</P>
<P>
   FBC-FSU-A&AMP;M _ EAST RUTHERFORD, N.J. _ Coverage of Florida State
vs. Texas A&AMP;M in the Pigskin Classic, 8 p.m. (Barnhart, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution)
</P>
