<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-08-31 19:36 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A1611 &Cx1f; tad-z
u v &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-ADVISORIES01-COX     08-31 0054
</HEADER>
