   _ The New Yorker's new editor,  &UR; David Remnick &LR; , will be
interviewed by  &UR; Orville Schell &LR;  for this November's  &UR; Herb Caen &LR; 
lecture at the University of California at Berkeley. High-tech
tycoon  &UR; Larry &LR;   &UR; Ellison &LR;  has agreed to talk with Schell onstage in
March.
</P>
