   _  &UR; Burt Bacharach &LR;  and &UR; Elvis Costello &LR;  are collaborators on
``Painted From Memory,'' an album to be released at the end of this
month Costello told Rolling Stone, ``This has nothing to do with
kitsch. ... It's great fun, and by all means get dressed up and
hold your martini glass, but don't mistake this for anything other
than very, very deeply felt music.''
</P>
