<P>
   A New York Times News Service article sent on Sunday, August 30,
had a headline about a dispute between Andersen Consulting and
J.Baker, a large apparel retailer, referred to the status of the
dispute incorrectly. As the article noted, J.Baker has not sued
Andersen; the consulting firm has sought a court ruling in an
effort to ward off a possible lawsuit by J.Baker.
</P>
