Photo)
</P>
<P>
   (NYT15) NEW YORK -- Aug. 31, 1998 -- GLAMOUR-EDITOR, 8-31 --
Ruth Whitney is stepping down after 31 years as the editor of
Glamour magazine. Under Mrs. Whitney's auspices, Glamour - a
middlebrow Conde Nast publication with a current circulation of 2.3
million - the magazine has addressed issues both homely and hot.
``I really wanted to make women feel good about themselves, not
