</HEADLINE>
 (Eds.: This quotation refers to BC-MARKET-VOICES-NYT, which moved
in ``f'' news file.) 
c.1998 N.Y. Times News Service   
<TEXT>
<P>
   ``It's like childbirth. It's not easy when you're going through
it, but after the pains your whole life is better. The party's not
over for me.''
</P>
<P>
   _JOSEPHINE McARTHUR, an investor from Stamford, Conn., on the
plunge in stock market prices.
</P>
